          "type": "text",
          "content": "Inline math with **KaTeX**: the Cauchy integral formula $f(a) = \\frac{1}{2\\pi i} \\oint_{\\gamma} \\frac{f(z)}{z - a} \\, dz$ renders seamlessly in text.",
          "position": { "x": 60, "y": 90 },
