          "content": "**Schrödinger Equation**\n\n$$\ni\\hbar \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}\\Psi(\\mathbf{r},t) = \\left[-\\frac{\\hbar^2}{2m}\\nabla^2 + V(\\mathbf{r},t)\\right]\\Psi(\\mathbf{r},t)\n$$",
