          "content": "**Einstein Field Equations**\n\n$$\nR_{\\mu\\nu} - \\tfrac{1}{2}R\\,g_{\\mu\\nu} + \\Lambda g_{\\mu\\nu} = \\frac{8\\pi G}{c^4}T_{\\mu\\nu}\n$$",
