        {
          "id": "e6",
          "type": "text",
          "content": "**Maxwell's Equations (differential form)**\n\n$$\n\\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf{E} = \\frac{\\rho}{\\varepsilon_0}, \\quad \\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf{B} = 0, \\quad \\nabla \\times \\mathbf{E} = -\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf{B}}{\\partial t}, \\quad \\nabla \\times \\mathbf{B} = \\mu_0\\mathbf{J} + \\mu_0\\varepsilon_0\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf{E}}{\\partial t}\n$$",
